She's just like the other juggernauts {{champion:86}} {{champion:122}} {{champion:82}} 

Like yes of course if you just let her walk up to you and use her skills she's gonna destroy you. Meanwhile she has literally zero mobility and can be kited to all hell. 

But this community doesn't bother trying to counterbuild/counterplay/counterpick them and then complains they're "OP"

It's the same thing with any hyper mobile champ {{champion:238}} {{champion:7}} {{champion:92}} {{champion:157}} 

instead of playing things that are good against them {{champion:1}} {{champion:90}} {{champion:127}} 

they pick immobile squishy champs without reliable CC and get destroyed, then complain that the champions DESIGNED to beat them are too strong.
